Kane County Chronicle Week 8 football live stream Published: Friday, Oct. 16, 2015 4:56 p.m. CDT Caption (Shaw Media file photo) Geneva's student section gets rowdy during last season's football game at Batavia. The teams meet tonight at Geneva's Burgess Field. By KANE COUNTY CHRONICLE - sportsdesk@kcchronicle.com
